data.description: One one-bedroom, one-bath condo nestled in a serene, gated community. This residence is enhanced by the community's amenities, including two pools, two clubhouses, and a tennis court. The condo boasts a scenic area near the water, offering a tranquil setting for relaxation. One assigned parking space and guest parking available. Low maintenance fee, this property stands out as an exceptional investment opportunity, especially for those seeking to rent immediately after purchase. Okay to lease 1st year. Don't miss the chance to own this exquisite, ready-to-rent condo, ideal for both personal enjoyment and investment.
